---
---

<section class="networking-section">
	<div class="section-content">
		<h2>Networking Infrastructure</h2>
		<p class="section-description">
			Secure, distributed network architectures that just work. Choose the approach 
			that fits your needs—managed simplicity or complete control.
		</p>
		
		<div class="options-grid">
			<!-- Managed Option -->
			<div class="option-card managed">
				<div class="option-icon-large">
					<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="64" height="64">
						<path d="M12 6a6 6 0 1 0 0 12 6 6 0 0 0 0-12Zm0 10a4 4 0 1 1 0-8 4 4 0 0 1 0 8Zm6-10a2 2 0 1 0 0 4 2 2 0 0 0 0-4Zm0 4.5a.5.5 0 1 1 0-1 .5.5 0 0 1 0 1ZM6 4a2 2 0 1 0 0 4 2 2 0 0 0 0-4Zm0 4.5a.5.5 0 1 1 0-1 .5.5 0 0 1 0 1Zm12 7a2 2 0 1 0 0 4 2 2 0 0 0 0-4Zm0 4.5a.5.5 0 1 1 0-1 .5.5 0 0 1 0 1ZM6 13a2 2 0 1 0 0 4 2 2 0 0 0 0-4Zm0 4.5a.5.5 0 1 1 0-1 .5.5 0 0 1 0 1ZM21 12a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Zm0-9a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Zm0 18a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0ZM3 12a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Zm0-9a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Zm0 18a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Z"/>
				</svg>
				</div>
				<div class="option-header">
					<h3>Zero-Config Simplicity</h3>
					<span class="option-badge">Managed</span>
				</div>
				<p>
					Let Tailscale handle the infrastructure. Get a secure WireGuard mesh network 
					up and running in minutes with SSO integration, MagicDNS, and automatic NAT traversal.
				</p>
				<ul class="option-features">
					<li>Works with GitHub, Google, Okta, Microsoft</li>
					<li>No firewall rules to configure</li>
					<li>Automatic key rotation</li>
					<li>Great for small to medium teams</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			
			<!-- Self-Hosted Option -->
			<div class="option-card self-hosted">
				<div class="option-icon-large self-hosted-icon">
					<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" width="64" height="64">
						<rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="6" rx="2"/>
						<rect x="2" y="15" width="20" height="6" rx="2"/>
						<path d="M6 6h.01M6 18h.01M12 6h.01M12 18h.01M18 6h.01M18 18h.01"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<div class="option-header">
					<h3>Own Your Infrastructure</h3>
					<span class="option-badge">Self-Hosted</span>
				</div>
				<p>
					Deploy NetBird or custom WireGuard on your own servers. Full control over 
					data, authentication, and network topology. Perfect for security-conscious 
					organizations and compliance requirements.
				</p>
				<ul class="option-features">
					<li>Data never leaves your infrastructure</li>
					<li>Custom identity providers</li>
					<li>Air-gapped network support</li>
					<li>Audit logging & compliance</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
		
		<p class="section-footer">
			Both solutions run on <strong>WireGuard</strong> — modern, fast, and battle-tested cryptography.
		</p>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.networking-section {
		padding: 4rem 0;
		border-top: 1px solid rgb(var(--gray-light));
	}

	.section-content {
		text-align: center;
	}

	h2 {
		font-size: 2rem;
		margin: 0 0 1rem;
	}

	.section-description {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
		max-width: 600px;
		margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
	}

	.options-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		text-align: left;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.option-card {
		background: var(--bg-color);
		border: 2px solid rgb(var(--gray-light));
		border-radius: 16px;
		padding: 2rem;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
	}

	.option-card:hover {
		border-color: var(--accent);
		transform: translateY(-4px);
		box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
	}

	.option-icon-large {
		color: var(--accent);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		opacity: 0.9;
	}

	.option-icon-large.self-hosted-icon {
		color: rgb(var(--gray));
	}

	.option-icon-large svg {
		display: block;
	}

	.option-header {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: center;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
		gap: 0.5rem;
	}

	.option-header h3 {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		margin: 0;
		color: var(--heading-color);
	}

	.option-badge {
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
		padding: 0.35rem 0.75rem;
		background: rgb(var(--gray-light));
		color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
		border-radius: 20px;
		white-space: nowrap;
	}

	.option-card > p {
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
		margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
		line-height: 1.5;
		flex: 1;
	}

	.option-features {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
	}

	.option-features li {
		padding: 0.35rem 0;
		padding-left: 1.25rem;
		position: relative;
	}

	.option-features li::before {
		content: "✓";
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		color: var(--accent);
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.section-footer {
		font-size: 1rem;
		color: rgb(var(--gray));
		margin: 0;
	}

	@media (max-width: 720px) {
		.options-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
